odd.head: General note
odd.p: Forms part of Yale Record Group 3-B (YRG 3-B), Records of Yale deputy, associate, and assistant provosts.

acqinfo.head: Immediate Source of Acquisition
acqinfo.p: The records were transferred from the Office of the Provost, 2007 and 2015.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: Access to the materials is restricted. See Collection Contents for details.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Deputy Provost for Science and Technology, Yale University, Records (RU 1054). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: The records are arranged alphabetically by topic.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The records consist of correspondence, reports, and topical files maintained by the office of the Deputy Provost for Science and Technology.
